// Syncthing ignore patterns for ~/.claude/projects/
// Goal: sync ONLY <project-slug>/memory/** subdirs.
// First match wins, so re-include patterns must come BEFORE the catch-all '*'.

// Per-machine transient state — Claude Code's memory-edit lock files. Ignore even inside memory/.
**/*.consolidate-lock

// Re-include memory dirs and their contents.
!**/memory
!**/memory/**

// Catch-all: ignore everything else.
*
